title: Elliot Rodger  Retribution      - The Video game
description: Play as Elliot Rodger in his new video game for the PC called retribution in it you can earn points by killing all the stuck up blonds that come your way you can also smash into other cars & take down bikers & stab other people in each different level game is fun once you get the hang of it also has old school 1980s 1990s  16Bit looking graphics   & music & game also contains real audio of Rodgers voice from his YouTube videos  as well while you play fun to play so please seed & share around thank you.
